    <div class="pg-code-block"><button class="pg-code-copy" onclick="copyPgCode(this)">Copy</button><pre>&lt;!-- Inline with text --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Press &lt;kbd class="sui-kbd sui-kbd-sm"&gt;Esc&lt;/kbd&gt; to close the dialog.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;!-- Shortcut inline --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Save your work with
  &lt;span class="sui-kbd-group"&gt;
